      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">Moringa Powder Market Outlook 2026: Trends, Prices, and Sourcing</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Where the moringa market stands in 2026, where it is heading, and what buyers need to know about sourcing, pricing, and quality.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-brand-300">
        <span>March 23, 2026</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand-500"></span>
        <span>10 min read</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Article Content -->
